{"tid":1155214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【嫌卓林唔長進？】結婚半年疑玩完 老婆Andi：說再見好嗎","createTime":"2019-05-14T20:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T03:31:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e164f619e17e170c52090f60e15f5920c3b1a8e9","tid":1155214,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:28:45.000Z","msg":"成龍與吳綺莉的女兒吳卓林同女友Andi上年11月在IG公佈婚書，宣佈已經在加拿大結婚，二人強調結婚證書具法律效力，又指已戰勝恐懼，追尋幸福（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2E3nD5t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E3nD5t&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=4b577535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2E3nD5t</a> ）。<br />\n雖然卓林和Andi「婚後」生活潦倒，試過因為欠租而驚動警方，最後要媽咪吳綺莉幫助代繳，不過未有影響兩人關係，直到昨日Andi突然在IG寫下長文，內容疑似是大罵吳卓林不長進，她說：「我討厭我仍然激勵你，我希望你好，但你甚至不試着做自己。你還有自己嗎？」 她還說：「當我無家可歸時，我拋開一切，我的心讓我定下來，所以我找到自己的方向，弄清楚你是怎樣的人。你稱你自己是豬，但你不想像我們一樣飛翔嗎？積極向上吧，不要老是跟在我屁股後面找答案。」最後她還說：「不要再管我了，最後說再見好嗎？」<br />\n但日前Andi亦曾經在IG晒合照兼留言：「好攰，一直說話到天亮，這是我們深夜的記憶，今晚很開心。」所以未知今次Andi的留言原因，今日《蘋果》曾向卓林了解，不過仍未有回覆。《蘋果》問吳綺莉卓林是否與Andi分手時，她說：「我做緊嘢唔方便講電話，你哋問番佢本人喇。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557816195_e78d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557816195_e78d.jpg&h=16551a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190514/59599093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599093&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=80280436\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599093&h=ddac0f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190514/59599093</a>"},{"pid":"a274da60c9cb05c2e927f5edb9f2f72c32981543","tid":1155214,"uid":280,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:42:00.000Z","msg":"戇撚尻⋯⋯佢咪又一樣 好撚長進咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e649f3b353e51c52795fe5d04d5d9fa64674c51e","tid":1155214,"uid":137569,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T21:06:31.000Z","msg":"估唔到個鬼妹識打中文"},{"pid":"11e61e1c5fa9380d853eee8390e0fc0b5dc98ece","tid":1155214,"uid":65984,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T21:08:42.000Z","msg":"屌. 大家都係女人, 點解要人地長進, 而自己唔長進, 咁叻咪賺錢養埋佢囉<br />\n根本就貪人老豆係國際巨星, 以為會有油水分, 依家分唔到就怪對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f53a9cdcf3da3e12ecf4fc2f48cdaeb994214a8","tid":1155214,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"係咪娛樂圈冇新聞 要攞呢隻死tb黎做新聞呀屌"},{"pid":"33b86a488d94e804f26d0fe5a4b7abeba1f6f32f","tid":1155214,"uid":119695,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"Audi：卓林攞唔到成龍副身家，唔長進！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086b20cbb90072398c88d7b6d49a135165005c11","tid":1155214,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"堆填區有臭味都係新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9a93a1083bdfdbd53abd408cdbaa44d6f1e499","tid":1155214,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"細細個吸老母負面情緒太多"},{"pid":"c3370bddc5d51e45b3fc2e4225fe861cfca2cf36","tid":1155214,"uid":154631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e164f619e17e170c52090f60e15f5920c3b1a8e9","tid":1155214,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:28:45.000Z","msg":"成龍與吳綺莉的女兒吳卓林同女友Andi上年11月在IG公佈婚書，宣佈已經在加拿大結婚，二人強調結婚證書具法律效力，又指已戰勝恐懼，追尋幸福（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2E3nD5t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.li