:1155214,"uid":54597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3370bddc5d51e45b3fc2e4225fe861cfca2cf36","tid":1155214,"uid":154631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e164f619e17e170c52090f60e15f5920c3b1a8e9","tid":1155214,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T20:28:45.000Z","msg":"成龍與吳綺莉的女兒吳卓林同女友Andi上年11月在IG公佈婚書，宣佈已經在加拿大結婚，二人強調結婚證書具法律效力，又指已戰勝恐懼，追尋幸福（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2E3nD5t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E3nD5t&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=4b577535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2E3nD5t</a> ）。<br />\n雖然卓林和Andi「婚後」生活潦倒，試過因為欠租而驚動警方，最後要媽咪吳綺莉幫助代繳，不過未有影響兩人關係，直到昨日Andi突然在IG寫下長文，內容疑似是大罵吳卓林不長進，她說：「我討厭我仍然激勵你，我希望你好，但你甚至不試着做自己。你還有自己嗎？」 她還說：「當我無家可歸時，我拋開一切，我的心讓我定下來，所以我找到自己的方向，弄清楚你是怎樣的人。你稱你自己是豬，但你不想像我們一樣飛翔嗎？積極向上吧，不要老是跟在我屁股後面找答案。」最後她還說：「不要再管我了，最後說再見好嗎？」<br />\n但日前Andi亦曾經在IG晒合照兼留言：「好攰，一直說話到天亮，這是我們深夜的記憶，今晚很開心。」所以未知今次Andi的留言原因，今日《蘋果》曾向卓林了解，不過仍未有回覆。《蘋果》問吳綺莉卓林是否與Andi分手時，她說：「我做緊嘢唔方便講電話，你哋問番佢本人喇。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557816195_e78d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557816195_e78d.jpg&h=16551a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190514/59599093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599093&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=80280436\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190514%2F59599093&h=ddac0f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190514/59599093</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"原來呢個世界真係有因果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},